response.overview: After kidnapping a father and his two kids, the Gecko brothers head south to a seedy Mexican bar to hide out in safety, unaware of its notorious vampire clientele.
response.tagline: One night is all that stands between them and freedom. But it's going to be a hell of a night.
response.title: From Dusk Till Dawn
